flowchart TD
    user[Пользователь CMDBuild] --> ui[CMDBuild Web UI]
    operator[Оператор интеграции] -->|HTTP :5090| monui[monitoring-ui-api :5090]
    monui -->|SAML2/OAuth2 + LDAP groups :443/:80/:636/:389| idp[IdP / MS AD]
    monui -->|CMDB REST catalog :8090| cmdb
    monui -->|Zabbix JSON-RPC catalog :8081| zabbix
    monui -->|local FS rules validate/upload| rules[(Git rules JSON)]
    monui -->|rules management save-as draft/webhook files| downloads[(Local downloads)]
    monui -->|GET /health :5080| wh
    monui -->|GET /health :5081| conv
    monui -->|GET /health :5082| api
    monui -->|GET /health :5083| bind
    monui -->|POST /admin/reload-rules :5081| conv
    monui -->|Kafka events read-only :9092| kafka
    ui -->|HTTP :8090| cmdb[CMDBuild :8090]
    cmdb -->|POST :5080 /webhooks/cmdbuild| wh[cmdbwebhooks2kafka :5080]
    wh -->|cmdbuild.webhooks.* :9092| kafka[(Kafka :9092)]
    kafka -->|consume cmdbuild.webhooks.* :9092| conv[cmdbkafka2zabbix :5081]
    conv -->|resolve cmdbPath reference/domain leaf :8090| cmdb
    rules --> conv
    conv -->|produce zabbix.host.requests.* :9092| kafka
    kafka -->|consume zabbix.host.requests.* :9092| api[zabbixrequests2api :5082]
    api -->|JSON-RPC :8081| zabbix[Zabbix API :8081]
    api -->|zabbix.host.responses.* :9092| kafka
    api -->|zabbix.host.bindings.* :9092| kafka
    kafka -->|consume zabbix.host.bindings.* :9092| bind[zabbixbindings2cmdbuild :5083]
    bind -->|write zabbix_main_hostid / ZabbixHostBinding :8090| cmdb
    wh -->|logs :9092| logs[Kafka log topics]
    conv -->|logs :9092| logs
    api -->|logs :9092| logs
    bind -->|logs :9092| logs
    logs -. future ship :9200 .-> elk[ELK]

    subgraph subprocesses[Повторно используемые подпроцессы]
        sp1[SP-001 webhook auth + normalize]
        sp2[SP-002 cmdbPath reference/domain resolver + rules + hostProfiles + regex + T4 conversion]
        sp3[SP-003 Zabbix payload validation]
        sp4[SP-004 host.get fallback]
        sp5[SP-005 JSON-RPC + response + state]
        sp6[SP-006 catalog sync]
        sp7[SP-007 rules validate + backup + save]
        sp8[SP-008 conversion rules add/delete + reference/domain drill-down + save-as]
        sp9[SP-009 UI language ru/en + Help/tooltips]
        sp11[SP-011 binding event + CMDBuild reverse write]
    end

    subgraph fallback[Fallback для update/delete без zabbix_hostid]
        api -->|host.get JSON-RPC :8081| zabbix
        api -->|host.update merge назначений или host.delete JSON-RPC :8081| zabbix
    end
